# This file will contain audit operation logs in JSONL format
# Each line is a JSON object with:
# - recorded_at: ISO timestamp
# - tool: tool name that performed the audit
# - module: module being audited
# - source_path: source codebase path
# - pattern_counts: object with counts per pattern type
# Example:
# {"recorded_at":"2026-04-06T10:00:00.000Z","tool":"scan_source_patterns","module":"deals","source_path":"/path/to/source","pattern_counts":{"vuex":5,"mixins":3}}
